title: EP.58: CAN THE PACKERS BOUNCE BACK, WILL TJ WATT SAVE THE STEELERS SEASON, LAKERS, NFL TRADES, AND MUCH MORE!
description: In this episode Griffin begs the packers to make a move while Joe hangs onto the very little hope he has about the steelers future. We discuss the lakers looking bad and the NFL trades that were made. We look into next weeks matchup and give our insights and predictions for week 8
